3. Major Weaknesses (Why this gets rejected today)
3.1 ❗ Insufficient Baselines (Critical)
You are missing the comparisons that reviewers require:

SGD + momentum + cosine decay (strongly tuned)
AdamW with matched training budget (not epochs)
Modern optimizer sweeps (grid or Bayesian tuned)

Right now, the result can be dismissed as:
“under-tuned baseline vs overfit new method”
3.2 ❗ Epochs ≠ Efficiency
Your central claim:
“3.5× fewer epochs”
This will be attacked immediately.
Because:

Wavelet transform adds compute
Kurtosis adds compute
CPU↔GPU transfers (!!) in your code

You even admit:
“10–20% overhead (estimate)”
That’s not enough.
What reviewers will say:
“Show wall-clock time or this claim is not valid.”
